NEW TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:5 "The §SPlanets and Sectors§! screen provides an overview of all our colonized worlds, their §SPops§!, and their §SResource Output§!. As our empire grows it can be organized into Sectors, which are helpful for administering larger empires.\n\n§SSectors§! can be automated here, and if they are automated they can be given a specialization and resources to enable planets within them to build and upgrade §SBuildings§! and §SDistricts§! on their planets."
OLD TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:4 "The §SPlanets and Sectors§! screen provides an overview of all our colonized worlds, their §SPops§!, and their §SResource Output§!. As our empire grows it will be automatically organized into §SSectors§!, which are vital to administering larger empires.\n\n§SSectors§! can be given resources and told to automatically build and upgrade §SBuildings§! and §SDistricts§! on their planets."
CN  TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:5 "§S行星和星域!界面显示了我们所有殖民星球的概览，包括其§人口§!和§S资源产出§!。随着帝国的发展，星球将自动组成§S星域§!，星域对于管理庞大的帝国至关重要。\n\n你可以为§S星域§!分配资源，并设置自动建造并升级行星上的§S建筑§!和§S地区§!。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:5 "§S星球与星域§!界面提供了我们所有殖民星球的概览，其§S人口§!，以及§S资源产出§!。随着帝国的发展，星球将可以被组成星域，这对管理庞大的帝国来说至关重要。\n\n§S星域§!可以在此处被设为自动分配，在自动模式下，星域可以设置模板并分配资源，以对其内行星进行建造并升级星球上的§S建筑§!与§S区划§!。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_PLANETS_DESC:5 "§S行星和星域§!界面提供了我们所有殖民星球的概览，包括其§S人口§!和§S资源产出§!。随着帝国的发展，星球可以被组成星域，这对管理庞大的帝国来说至关重要。\n\n§S星域§!可以在此处被设为自动分配，在自动模式下，星域可以设置专注并分配资源，以对其内行星进行建造并升级星球上的§S建筑§!和§S地区§!。"
NEW TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:3 "This is our homeworld and the §SCapital§! of our empire. The §SPlanet Summary§! screen, which we are currently looking at, provides an overview of the planet's important statistics.\n\nWe can see the total number of §SDistricts§! this planet can support, how many §SPops§! are living on it, and how much §SFood§! and other §SResources§! it produces and consumes. We can also see if the planet is suffering from low §SStability§!, and if there is an assigned §SGovernor§!, they are found here. We may also set a designation, if desired, and have the option to automate the planet."
OLD TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:2 "This is our homeworld and the §SCapital§! of our empire. The §SPlanet Summary§! screen, which we are currently looking at, provides an overview of the planet's important statistics.\n\nWe can see the total number of §SDistricts§! this planet can support, how many §SPops§! are living on it, and how much §SFood§! and other §SResources§! it produces and consumes. We can also see if the planet is suffering from low §SStability§!, and if there is an assigned §SGovernor§!, they are found here."
CN  TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:3 "这是我们的母星，也是帝国的§S首都§!。我们现在看到的§S行星总览§!界面，显示了这颗行星的重要数据概览。\n\n我们可以看到这颗行星可以支持的§S地区§!总数，上面生活的§S人口§!数和行星生产消耗的§S食物§!及其它§S资源§!数量。我们也可以看到这颗行星的§S稳定度§!是否过低。而且如果指派了§S总督§!，也会显示在这里。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:3 "这是我们的母星，也是帝国的§S首都§!。我们目前正在浏览的是§S星球总览§!界面，显示了星球的重要统计数据。\n\n我们可以看到这颗星球可以支持的§S区划§!总数，上面住着多少§S人口§!，以及生产和消耗多少§S食物§!与其它§S资源§!。我们也可以看到这颗星球的§S稳定性§!是否过低，而且如果指派了§S总督§!，也会显示在这里。我们也可以在需要时设置行星规划类型，并自动对行星进行建造。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_PLANETVIEW_PLANET_DESC:3 "这是我们的母星，也是帝国的§S首都§!。我们目前正在浏览的是§S行星总览§!界面，显示了这颗行星的重要数据概览。\n\n我们可以看到这颗行星可以支持的§S地区§!总数，上面生活的§S人口§!数和行星生产消耗的§S食物§!及其它§S资源§!数量。我们也可以看到这颗行星的§S稳定度§!是否过低。而且如果指派了§S总督§!，也会显示在这里。我们也可以在需要时设置行星规划，自动建设行星。"
NEW TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:2 "To establish a §SSector§!, first select a planet in §SFrontier space§! and press the Create Sector button. This will make the planet the §SCapital§! of a new Sector and all frontier space systems within six hyperjumps will be added to it. Sectors may automate the construction of planetary buildings on planets within them if this option is enabled and they are given resources, greatly reducing the need for micromanagement."
OLD TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:1 "In §SSector Management Mode§!, planets are added to new or existing §SSectors§! on a per-system basis, for a slight £influence£ §SInfluence§! cost.\n\n§SSectors§! automate the construction of planetary buildings, greatly reducing the need for micromanagement, and can be tasked with specific production focuses and assigned different tax rates."
CN  TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:2 "在§S星域管理模式§!中，把相邻的行星添加到新的或已有的§S星域§!里，按照每个星系的基准需要花费少量的£influence£ §S影响力§!。\n\n§S星域§!使行星建筑的建造实现自动化，极大减少微观管理。还可以按照具体的侧重点进行生产以及分配不同的税率。"
CN2 TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:2 "要建立一个§S星域§!，首先选中一颗在§S边境区域§!的行星并按下创建星域按钮。这会以此行星作为新星域的§S首府§!，所有在六次超空间跳跃内的边境区域恒星系都会被添加到此星域。星域在启动自动模式并给予资源后可以自动进行行星建筑物建造，极大减少了微观管理。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_CREATESECTOR_DESC:2 "要建立一个§S星域§!，首先选中一颗位于§S边境太空§!的行星并按下创建星域按钮。这将以此行星作为新星域的§S治所§!，所有在六次超空间跃迁距离内的边境太空星系都会被添加到此星域。星域在启动自动模式并给予资源后可以自动建设行星建筑，极大减少了微观管理。"
NEW tutorial.44.desc:1 "Our burgeoning empire has now reached a size where it is becoming difficult to administer directly from our homeworld. We should establish a new §SSector§!.\n\nSectors are areas within our empire that can be set to independently manage the day-to-day affairs of the planets under their jurisdiction."
OLD tutorial.44.desc:0 "Our burgeoning empire has now reached a size where it is becoming difficult to administer directly from our homeworld. We should establish a new §SSector§!.\n\nSectors are semi-autonomous entities within our empire that independently manage the day-to-day affairs of the planets under their jurisdiction."
CN  tutorial.44.desc:1 "我们的帝国蓬勃发展，规模已经大到我们没法通过母星直接进行控制了。我们应该建立新的 §S星域§!。\n\n星域实行半自治制度，在他们的权限范围内可以自行负责日常的事务。"
CN2 tutorial.44.desc:1 "我们的帝国蓬勃发展，规模已经大到我们没法通过母星直接进行控制了。我们应该建立新的§S星域§!。\n\n星域使用半自理模式，居民可以在他们的权限范围内自行负责日常的事务。"
CHANGE tutorial.44.desc:1 "我帝国蓬勃发展，规模已经大到我们没法通过母星直接进行控制了。我们应该建立新的§S星域§!。\n\n星域是帝国的半自治实体，在他们的权限范围内自行负责日常事务。"
NEW tutorial.45.desc:2 "As our empire grows, new colonies can be organized into §SSectors§!. Sectors can be automated from the §SPlanets and Sectors§! screen to automatically build and upgrade Districts and Buildings using assigned pools of resources."
OLD tutorial.45.desc:1 "As our empire grows, new colonies will automatically be organized into §SSectors§!. Sectors can be managed from the §SPlanets and Sectors§! screen to automatically build and upgrade Districts and Buildings using assigned pools of Minerals and Energy."
CN  tutorial.45.desc:2 "随着帝国的发展，新殖民地将自动组成§S星域§!。星域可以在§S行星和星域§!界面进行管理，设置利用分配的矿物和能源点数，自动建造并升级地区和建筑。"
CN2 tutorial.45.desc:2 "随着帝国的发展，新的殖民地可以被划归进§S星域§!。星域可以在§S星球与星域§!界面进行自动管理，自动对区划与建筑进行建造与升级。"
CHANGE tutorial.45.desc:2 "随着帝国的发展，新殖民地可以归入§S星域§!。星域可以在§S行星和星域§!界面设置为自动管理，利用分配的资源，自动建造并升级地区和建筑。"
